reviewText: This series is very dark with no positive upside.  I must admit we gave up and didn't finish it.
Depressing suicide of one of the main characters.  Didn't seem likely to happen .Don't know if I will watch it again

This movie was very good.  It had twists that you might not expect but the story & characters are very good.  I watched this, my boss watched it & her parents watched it.  we all liked it & are of varying ages.
